config BMA250_ACC_DRIVER
	tristate "YAS Acceleration Sensor- BMA250"
	depends on I2C
	help
	  Say Y here if you want support for the BMA250 sensor
	  device.

	  To compile this driver as a module, choose M here: the
	  module will be called BMA250.


